title: 2015 Viking FK season
text:
The <a href="2015%20Tippeligaen">2015 season</a> was <a href="Viking%20FK">Viking's</a> third full season with <a href="Kjell%20Jonevret">Kjell Jonevret</a> as manager. They are competing in the <a href="2015%20Tippeligaen">Tippeligaen</a> and the <a href="2015%20Norwegian%20Football%20Cup">cup</a>.
